Description: A Wolf Pelt will protect you from one night kill, but it will make you appear as a Werewolf to the Seer

A war spear can kill a player at night, but it is heavy and unwieldy so you will roleblock yourself if you choose to use it. It can only be used once. Protection will stop the kill, and if the Huntsman catches you trying to kill someone they are guarding, you will both die.

A Sjón Rune allows you to check a player's alignment. Holding it will make you appear as a Witch Craft user to intel checks. After use, a Rune must recharge and can be used again by you three nights later. If you pass the Rune to a different player they will be able to use it immediately.
A Potion of Acquiescence can be used once to steal any items the target player has
An Iron Collar can save you from a single lynch.

The Amulet of Peace will roleblock you if you have killing status. It will roleblock anyone that visits you if they have killing status. During the day, your vote will carry no weight. If you hold the amulet and have the most votes, it will save you from being lynched. The Amulet of Peace must be passed to a different player each night.
